  "title": "Inside Sales Coordinator (Pump Control)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Support the sales team in preparing and sending quotations to clients.</li>\n  <li>Follow up on pending quotations to ensure timely responses.</li>\n  <li>Handle initial customer inquiries regarding quotations and escalate complex or technical questions to the appropriate sales or technical team members.</li>\n  <li>Assist the sales team in tracking their sales pipeline and monitoring individual performance targets.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate urgent orders by liaising with the warehouse and service teams to ensure prompt delivery.</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with the warehouse and service teams on high-value or complex orders to ensure accurate fulfillment.</li>\n  <li>Provide general administrative and operational support to sales representatives while they are in the field.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma in Business Administration or any related field.</li>\n  <li>Minimum 2 years in administration and sales coordination</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication, negotiation and presentation skills</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Interested applicants for the above advertised position(s), please kindly email an updated copy of your resume to: <strong>gs1@talenttradersg.com;</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>EA License No.: 13C6305</p>\n<p>Registration No.: R23117856 CHOE KIN MUN</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>For candidate who applied for the advertised position is deemed to have consented to us that we may collect, use or disclose your personal information for purpose in connection with the services provided by us.</p>",
